# Browser-visible API origin (no trailing slash). Build-time for Vite.
# Local — must match your backend listen address (see backend PORT in .env):
VITE_API_URL=http://localhost:3000
#
# Production build (npm run build): must use HTTPS (see vite.config.ts).
# Copy frontend/.env.production.example to .env.production or set VITE_API_URL in CI.
# Example:
# VITE_API_URL=https://api.nezhin.cc
